  "title": "14 Seater School Bus Driver (with Teacher Assistant Duties)",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re Hiring: School Bus Driver (with Teacher Assistant\nDuties)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong>We are looking for a <strong>responsible\nand caring School Bus Driver</strong> to join our preschool near <strong>Potong\nPasir MRT</strong>. This role combines safe transport duties with supporting our\nteachers in the classroom.<strong>Daily Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Driving Duties (Approx. 2 hours/day):</strong>Safely operate a\n14-seater minibus on pre-planned school routes.<br />\nSend and fetch preschoolers between home and school.<br />\nEnsure punctual pickup and drop-off of children.<br />\nAlways ensure the safety and well-being of children on board.<br />\nAdhere strictly to all traffic laws and safety guidelines.</p><p><strong>Teacher Assistant Duties (When not driving):</strong>Assist\nteachers with classroom routines and activities.<br />\nSupport in supervising children during playtime or transitions.<br />\nHelp with simple school errands or logistics as needed.</p><p><strong>Vehicle Maintenance & Reporting:</strong>Conduct daily\nbasic vehicle checks (fuel, brakes, tires, lights, etc.).<br />\nKeep the bus clean and well-maintained.<br />\nReport any issues or damages promptly to management.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p><br />\n<strong>Location:</strong> Near Potong Pasir MRT</p><p><br />\n<strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time or Part-time (5 days per week)</p><p><br />\n<strong>License:</strong> Valid Class 3 Driving License with BDVL</p><p><br />\n<strong>Clean driving record</strong> (no major violations in the past 2 years)<br />\nPhysically fit, alert, and enjoys working with children<br />\nResponsible, punctual, and a team player</p><p>If you’re someone who loves working around children and\ntakes pride in driving safely — we’d love to hear from you!</p>",
